OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The BBC has apologised for the way it  
OL,6, handled a complaint about the presenter
OL,7, Huw Edwards.                           
OL,9,FAllegations about his behaviour were   
OL,10,Fmade in May 2023 but did not reach     
OL,11,Fsenior managers until 6 July.          
OL,13,FThe corporation said the complaint was 
OL,14,Fnot "escalated quickly enough" and that
OL,15,Fit has now changed its processes.      
OL,17,FAn independent report by Deloitte into 
OL,18,Fthe BBC's complaints handling procedure
OL,19,Fsaid a complaint by the family of a    
OL,20,Fyoung person was made on the 18 May.   
